HCPCSCodeForm is a Form
    is primary
    title is "HCPCSCode"
    Layout
        paragraph
            visible when (not RecordExists)
                HCPCSCode.HCPCS
                HCPCSCode.Sequence
            visible when (RecordExists)
                display as text
                    HCPCSCode.HCPCS
                    HCPCSCode.Sequence
            DisplayHCPCSCode
                label is "HCPCSAndSequence"
                display as text
        single column
            RecordID
            ShortDescription
            LongDescription
                use text area of 4 lines
